# Portfolio Content Blocks — Visual Reference Guide

> **For the Content Team**: This document explains every available block, what data you need to provide, and how it looks on the website.

---

## How It Works

Each portfolio project has a `content` array. Each item in the array is a **block** with a `type` field. You compose a portfolio page by stacking blocks in any order.

```json
{
  "content": [
    { "type": "hero", ... },
    { "type": "text-highlight", ... },
    { "type": "info-card", ... }
  ]
}
```

> [!IMPORTANT]
> All text fields support **localization**. You can pass either a plain string `"Hello"` or an object `{ "en": "Hello", "ge": "გამარჯობა" }`.

