## 1. Hero Block

**Type**: `hero` · **Purpose**: Full-screen intro section with background media. Usually the first block.

![Hero Block — Center Aligned](C:/Users/User/.gemini/antigravity/brain/95306e18-9900-4d81-8437-b355e45affa2/01_hero_center_1771540956533.png)

### Data Structure

```json
{
  "type": "hero",
  "media": "/images/project/cover.jpg",
  "mediaType": "image",
  "title": { "en": "Project Title", "ge": "პროექტის სახელი" },
  "subtitle": { "en": "Category / Client", "ge": "კატეგორია / კლიენტი" },
  "badge": { "en": "Social Media", "ge": "სოციალური მედია" },
  "align": "center"
}
```

| Field | Required | Options | Description |
|---|---|---|---|
| `media` | ✅ | image/video path | Background media |
| `mediaType` | ✅ | `"image"` or `"video"` | Type of media |
| `title` | Optional | text | Large heading |
| `subtitle` | Optional | text | Smaller text above title |
| `badge` | Optional | text | Pill-shaped tag above subtitle |
| `align` | Optional | `"center"` (default) or `"left"` | Text alignment |

