## 2. Text Highlight Block

**Type**: `text-highlight` · **Purpose**: Important statements, chapter titles, or section text.

### Center Aligned

![Text Highlight — Center](C:/Users/User/.gemini/antigravity/brain/95306e18-9900-4d81-8437-b355e45affa2/02_text_center_1771540957613.png)

### Left Aligned

![Text Highlight — Left](C:/Users/User/.gemini/antigravity/brain/95306e18-9900-4d81-8437-b355e45affa2/03_text_left_1771540964616.png)

### Data Structure

```json
{
  "type": "text-highlight",
  "label": { "en": "The Challenge", "ge": "გამოწვევა" },
  "text": { "en": "Your main statement here...", "ge": "თქვენი ტექსტი..." },
  "align": "center"
}
```

| Field | Required | Options | Description |
|---|---|---|---|
| `text` | ✅ | text | Main paragraph content |
| `label` | Optional | text | Small uppercase label above text |
| `align` | Optional | `"center"` (default) or `"left"` | Text alignment |

