## 3. Legacy Columns Block

**Type**: `legacy-columns` · **Purpose**: Two-column layout for "Challenge vs Strategy" or similar comparisons.

![Legacy Columns](C:/Users/User/.gemini/antigravity/brain/95306e18-9900-4d81-8437-b355e45affa2/04_legacy_columns_1771540965688.png)

### Data Structure

```json
{
  "type": "legacy-columns",
  "left": {
    "label": { "en": "The Task", "ge": "ამოცანა" },
    "title": { "en": "Challenge", "ge": "გამოწვევა" },
    "text": { "en": "Describe the problem...", "ge": "აღწერეთ პრობლემა..." }
  },
  "right": {
    "label": { "en": "The Strategy", "ge": "სტრატეგია" },
    "title": { "en": "Our Approach", "ge": "ჩვენი მიდგომა" },
    "text": { "en": "Describe the solution...", "ge": "აღწერეთ გადაწყვეტა..." }
  }
}
```

| Field | Required | Description |
|---|---|---|
| `left.title` | ✅ | Left column heading |
| `left.text` | ✅ | Left column paragraph |
| `left.label` | Optional | Small label above heading |
| `right.*` | Same as left | Right column content |

