## 5. Media Grid Block

**Type**: `media-grid` · **Purpose**: Gallery of images/videos in a grid layout.

### Square Items (2 columns)

![Media Grid — Square](C:/Users/User/.gemini/antigravity/brain/95306e18-9900-4d81-8437-b355e45affa2/09_mediagrid_square_1771540979470.png)

### Wide Item (full width)

![Media Grid — Wide](C:/Users/User/.gemini/antigravity/brain/95306e18-9900-4d81-8437-b355e45affa2/10_mediagrid_wide_1771540980898.png)

### Mixed (squares + wide)

![Media Grid — Mixed](C:/Users/User/.gemini/antigravity/brain/95306e18-9900-4d81-8437-b355e45affa2/11_mediagrid_mixed_v2_1771541045998.png)

### Data Structure

```json
{
  "type": "media-grid",
  "items": [
    { "media": "/images/photo1.jpg", "mediaType": "image", "size": "sq" },
    { "media": "/images/photo2.jpg", "mediaType": "image", "size": "sq" },
    { "media": "/images/wide.jpg", "mediaType": "image", "size": "wide" }
  ]
}
```

| Field | Required | Options | Description |
|---|---|---|---|
| `items[].media` | ✅ | path | Image or video path |
| `items[].mediaType` | ✅ | `"image"` / `"video"` | Type |
| `items[].size` | Optional | `"sq"` (default) or `"wide"` | `sq` = one column, `wide` = full width |

