## 6. Reel Grid Block

**Type**: `reel-grid` · **Purpose**: Vertical 9:16 cards, perfect for Reels/TikTok/Stories content.

![Reel Grid](C:/Users/User/.gemini/antigravity/brain/95306e18-9900-4d81-8437-b355e45affa2/12_reelgrid_1771540983592.png)

### Data Structure

```json
{
  "type": "reel-grid",
  "mobileLayout": "swipe",
  "items": [
    { "media": "/images/reel1.mp4", "mediaType": "video", "caption": { "en": "Behind the Scenes", "ge": "კულისებს მიღმა" } },
    { "media": "/images/reel2.mp4", "mediaType": "video", "caption": { "en": "Product Demo", "ge": "პროდუქტის დემო" } },
    { "media": "/images/reel3.mp4", "mediaType": "video", "caption": { "en": "Testimonial", "ge": "შეფასება" } }
  ]
}
```

| Field | Required | Options | Description |
|---|---|---|---|
| `mobileLayout` | Optional | `"swipe"` or `"column"` | `swipe` = horizontal scroll on mobile, `column` = stacked |
| `items[].media` | ✅ | path | Media path |
| `items[].mediaType` | ✅ | `"image"` / `"video"` | Type |
| `items[].caption` | Optional | text | Caption overlay at the bottom |

