## 8. Vertical Showcase Block

**Type**: `vertical-showcase` · **Purpose**: Single tall vertical media, great for mobile app screenshots or portrait content.

![Vertical Showcase](C:/Users/User/.gemini/antigravity/brain/95306e18-9900-4d81-8437-b355e45affa2/14_vertical_showcase_1771540986229.png)

### Data Structure

```json
{
  "type": "vertical-showcase",
  "media": "/images/mobile-screen.jpg",
  "mediaType": "image",
  "title": { "en": "App Design", "ge": "აპის დიზაინი" },
  "overlayText": { "en": "Award-winning UX", "ge": "ჯილდოს მფლობელი UX" }
}
```

| Field | Required | Options | Description |
|---|---|---|---|
| `media` | ✅ | path | Image or video |
| `mediaType` | ✅ | `"image"` / `"video"` | Type |
| `title` | Optional | text | Bold heading at the bottom |
| `overlayText` | Optional | text | Smaller text under the title |

