## 9. Results Block

**Type**: `results` · **Purpose**: Displaying campaign outcomes with big numbers.

![Results Block](C:/Users/User/.gemini/antigravity/brain/95306e18-9900-4d81-8437-b355e45affa2/15_results_v2_1771541016632.png)

### Data Structure

```json
{
  "type": "results",
  "title": { "en": "Campaign Results", "ge": "კამპანიის შედეგები" },
  "description": { "en": "Our strategy delivered...", "ge": "ჩვენმა სტრატეგიამ..." },
  "stats": [
    { "label": { "en": "Engagement", "ge": "ჩართულობა" }, "value": { "en": "150%", "ge": "150%" } },
    { "label": { "en": "Reach", "ge": "მიღწევა" }, "value": { "en": "500K+", "ge": "500K+" } },
    { "label": { "en": "Conversions", "ge": "კონვერსიები" }, "value": { "en": "12K", "ge": "12K" } },
    { "label": { "en": "ROI", "ge": "ROI" }, "value": { "en": "3.5x", "ge": "3.5x" } }
  ]
}
```

| Field | Required | Description |
|---|---|---|
| `title` | ✅ | Section heading |
| `description` | ✅ | Summary paragraph |
| `stats` | ✅ | Array of label/value metric pairs |

