## Quick Reference Table

| Block Type | Best For | Media? | Text? |
|---|---|---|---|
| `hero` | Page intro | ✅ Background | Title, Subtitle, Badge |
| `text-highlight` | Key statements | ❌ | Label + Text |
| `legacy-columns` | Challenge vs Strategy | ❌ | Two columns with title + text |
| `info-card` | Project details | ✅ Background | Title + key-value details |
| `media-grid` | Photo/video gallery | ✅ Grid items | ❌ |
| `reel-grid` | Reels/Stories showcase | ✅ Vertical items | Captions |
| `bento-grid` | Asymmetric highlight | ✅ Mixed sizes | Captions |
| `vertical-showcase` | Mobile/portrait content | ✅ Single vertical | Title + overlay text |
| `results` | Campaign metrics | ❌ | Title + stats |
